This place is just too much fun!  Chris Schimmel just reopened and remodeled the place, but the key is that his special energy attracted Mike Haynes, his manager, while keeping Denise and her following.  The bottom line is that the energy among both staff and clientele is accepting, uplifting, and too much fun at any time of day...  sure to be the newest and best local hotspot for anyone: gay, straight and anyone in between.  Butch bikers and delicate-types too. Early-birds, night-owls and most of all, fun-lovers... the more varied stripes the better.  Hit 'em up for a visit... you won't be disappointed and almost certainly will make a friend or two and for sure will be glad for the visit.  You'll be sure to fit in if smiles and lots of camarederie are your cup of tea, and if so certain to come back for more.
